                <h3>VTuber List</h3>
                <p>An app for finding and making lists of VTubers. Make a list of your favorite VTubers and share them with your friends so they can roast you for your bad taste. Search for VTubers by name, agency, or tags, or look up a bunch of random VTubers at once.</p>
                <p>This project is based on the movie watchlist assignment from Le Wagon and was built using Ruby on Rails and a template from Le Wagon. I did all of the coding and design.</p>
                <p>I made this app because I like discovering new, small VTubers, and I kept getting random VTubers recommended to me every time I opened up YouTube. At first, I kept saving their VODs to my playlists on YouTube, but after I had three playlists full of VTubers, I lost track of which ones I already added and which VTuber I put in which playlist.</p>
                <p>So then I decided to make this app so I could keep track of the VTubers I found.</p>
                <p>I entered all of the entries manually and picked out and cropped all of the pictures myself.</p>


